flowchart LR
    A[Data Sources] --> B[Ingest and Store]
    B --> C[Validate and Transform]
    C --> D[Feature Engineering]
    D --> E[Train and Tune]
    E --> F[Evaluate and Register]
    F --> G[Deploy]
    G --> H[Monitor Data, Model, and Infrastructure]
    H --> I{Drift, Bias, or Performance Issue?}
    I -- No --> H
    I -- Yes --> J[Trigger Retraining Workflow]
    J --> C

    B -. S3, Kinesis, DataSync .-> B
    C -. Glue, EMR, Data Wrangler .-> C
    D -. Feature Store .-> D
    E -. SageMaker Training and AMT .-> E
    F -. Clarify and Model Registry .-> F
    G -. Endpoints or Batch Transform .-> G
    H -. Model Monitor, CloudWatch, CloudTrail .-> H
